modules.sap/ui/demokit/explored/view/appSettings:
<core:FragmentDefinition
		xmlns="sap.m"
		xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout"
		xmlns:f="sap.ui.layout.form"
		xmlns:core="sap.ui.core">
	<Dialog
			title="Settings"
			class="sapUiPopupWithPadding"
			contentWidth="350px"
			id="AppSettingsDialog">
		<content>
			<l:Grid
					class="sapUiSmallMarginTop"
					hSpacing="0.5"
					vSpacing="0.5"
					defaultSpan="L6 M6 S10">
				<l:content>
					<Label text="Theme:" design="Standard" id="ThemeLabel">
						<layoutData>
							<l:GridData span="L12 M12 S12"/>
						</layoutData>
					</Label>

					<Select id="ThemeButtons" width="100%">
						<core:Item key="sap_hcb" text="High Contrast Black"/>
						<core:Item key="sap_bluecrystal" text="Blue Crystal"/>
						<layoutData>
							<l:GridData span="L12 M12 S12"/>
						</layoutData>
					</Select>

					<Label id="CompactModeLabel" text="Compact Form Factor:" design="Standard">
						<layoutData>
							<l:GridData span="L8 M8 S8"/>
						</layoutData>
					</Label>
					<Switch id="CompactModeButtons" state="false">
						<layoutData>
							<l:GridData span="L4 M4 S4"/>
						</layoutData>
					</Switch>

					<Label id="RTLLabel" text="Right To Left Mode:" design="Standard">
						<layoutData>
							<l:GridData span="L8 M8 S8"/>
						</layoutData>
					</Label>
					<Switch id="RTLButtons" state="false">
						<layoutData>
							<l:GridData span="L4 M4 S4"/>
						</layoutData>
					</Switch>
				</l:content>
			</l:Grid>
		</content>
		<beginButton>
			<Button text="OK" press="onSaveAppSettings"/>
		</beginButton>
		<endButton>
			<Button text="Cancel" press="onDialogCloseButton"/>
		</endButton>
	</Dialog>
</core:FragmentDefinition>
modules.sap/ui/demokit/explored/view/code.view.x:
<mvc:View
		controllerName="sap.ui.demokit.explored.view.code"
		xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc"
		xmlns:core="sap.ui.core"
		xmlns:l="sap.ui.layout"
		xmlns:d="sap.ui.demokit"
		xmlns="sap.m">
	<Page
			id="page"
			showNavButton="true"
			navButtonPress="onNavBack"
			title="{/title}"
			icon="img/144_iPad_Retina_Web_Clip.png" >
		<headerContent>
			<Button
					class="sapUiHideOnPhone"
					text="Download"
					icon="sap-icon://download"
					press="onDownload" />
			<Button
					class="sapUiVisibleOnlyOnPhone"
					icon="sap-icon://download"
					press="onDownload" />
		</headerContent>
		<content>
			<IconTabBar
					class="sapUiContentPadding"
					expandable="false"
					selectedKey="{/fileName}"
					select="handleTabSelectEvent"
					items="{/files}" >
				<items>
					<IconTabFilter
							key="{name}"
							text="{name}" >
						<content>
							<d:CodeViewer class="sapUiExploredCodeViewer" source="{raw}"/>
						</content>
					</IconTabFilter>
				</items>
			</IconTabBar>
		</content>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>
modules.sap/ui/demokit/explored/view/master.view:
<mvc:View
	controllerName="sap.ui.demokit.explored.view.master"
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc"
	xmlns="sap.m">
	<Page
		id="page" >
		<customHeader>
			<Toolbar>
				<Button icon="sap-icon://drop-down-list" id="viewSettingsButton" press="onOpenViewSettings" />
				<ToolbarSpacer/>
				<Title text="Entities ({entity>/entityCount})" />
				<ToolbarSpacer/>
				<Button icon="sap-icon://action-settings" tooltip="{i18n>settings}" press="onOpenAppSettings" />
			</Toolbar>
		</customHeader>
		<subHeader>
			<Bar
				id="searchBar">
				<contentMiddle>
					<SearchField
						id="searchField"
						placeholder="Search"
						liveChange="onSearch"
						width="100%" >
					</SearchField>
				</contentMiddle>
			</Bar>
		</subHeader>
		<content>
			<List
				id="list"
				class="myList"
				noDataText="{i18n>masterListNoData}"
				mode="{device>/listMode}"
				selectionChange="onNavToEntity"
				items="{
					path: 'entity>/entities',
					groupHeaderFactory: '.getGroupHeader',
					sorter: [{
						path: 'category',
						descending: false,
						group: true
					},{
						path: 'name',
						descending: false
					}]
				}" >
				<infoToolbar>
					<Toolbar
						id="vsFilterBar"
						active="true"
						visible="false"
						press="onOpenViewSettings">
						<Label id="vsFilterLabel" />
					</Toolbar>
				</infoToolbar>
				<items>
					<StandardListItem
						title="{entity>name}"
						counter="{entity>sampleCount}"
						type="{device>/listItemType}"
						press="onNavToEntity" />
				</items>
			</List>
		</content>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>
modules.sap/ui/demokit/explored/view/notFound.vi:
<mvc:View
	controllerName="sap.ui.demokit.explored.view.notFound"
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc"
	xmlns:core="sap.ui.core"
	xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
	xmlns="sap.m">
	<Page
		title="Not Found"
		showNavButton="{device>/isPhone}"
		navButtonPress="onNavBack"
		enableScrolling="false"
		class="titlesSpace" >
		<content>
			<core:HTML
				id="msgHtml"
				sanitizeContent="true" />
		</content>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>
modules.sap/ui/demokit/explored/view/sample.view:
<mvc:View
	controllerName="sap.ui.demokit.explored.view.sample"
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc"
	xmlns="sap.m">
	<Page
		id="page"
		showNavButton="{/showNavButton}"
		navButtonPress="onNavBack" >
		<headerContent>
			<Button
				id="prevSample"
				icon="sap-icon://navigation-up-arrow"
				class="sapUiHideOnPhone"
				tooltip="{i18n>samplePreviousTooltip}"
				enabled="{= ${/previousSampleId} !== undefined }"
				press="onPreviousSample"/>
			<Button
				id="nextSample"
				icon="sap-icon://navigation-down-arrow"

modules.sap/ui/demokit/explored/view/viewSetting:
<core:FragmentDefinition
	xmlns="sap.m"
	xmlns:core="sap.ui.core">
	<ViewSettingsDialog
		id="viewSettingsDialog"
		confirm="onConfirmViewSettings">
		<groupItems>
			<ViewSettingsItem text="{i18n>itemName}" key="name" selected="true" />
			<ViewSettingsItem text="{i18n>itemCategory}" key="category" />
			<ViewSettingsItem text="{i18n>itemFormFactors}" key="formFactors" />
			<ViewSettingsItem text="{i18n>itemNamespace}" key="namespace" />
			<ViewSettingsItem text="{i18n>itemSince}" key="since" />
		</groupItems>
		<filterItems>
			<ViewSettingsFilterItem
				text="{i18n>itemCategory}"
				key="category"
				id="categoryFilter"
				items="{
					path:'filter>/category',
					sorter: {
						path: 'filter>id',
						descending: false
					}
				}" >
				<items>
					<ViewSettingsItem text="{filter>id}" key="{filter>id}" />
				</items>
			</ViewSettingsFilterItem>
			<ViewSettingsFilterItem
				text="{i18n>itemFormFactors}"
				key="formFactors"
				items="{
					path:'filter>/formFactors',
					sorter: {
						path: 'filter>id',
						descending: false
					}
				}" >
				<items>
					<ViewSettingsItem text="{filter>id}" key="{filter>id}" />
				</items>
			</ViewSettingsFilterItem>
			<ViewSettingsFilterItem
				text="{i18n>itemNamespace}"
				key="namespace"
				items="{
					path:'filter>/namespace',
					sorter: {
						path: 'filter>id',
						descending: false
					}
				}" >
				<items>
					<ViewSettingsItem text="{filter>id}" key="{filter>id}" />
				</items>
			</ViewSettingsFilterItem>
			<ViewSettingsFilterItem
				text="{i18n>itemSince}"
				key="since"
				items="{
					path:'filter>/since',
					sorter: {
						path: 'filter>id',
						descending: false
					}
				}" >
				<items>
					<ViewSettingsItem text="{filter>id}" key="{filter>id}" />
				</items>
			</ViewSettingsFilterItem>
		</filterItems>
	</ViewSettingsDialog>
</core:FragmentDefinition>

modules.sap/ui/demokit/icex/view/Favorite.view.x:
<mvc:View controllerName="sap.ui.demokit.icex.view.Favorite"
	xmlns="sap.m"
	xmlns:core="sap.ui.core"
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc"
	xmlns:control="control"
	xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
	<Page
		id="page"
		title="Favorites ({fav>/count})"
		showNavButton="{ui>/inDisplay}"
		navButtonPress="navBack"
		icon="{img>/icon/ui5}">
		<headerContent>
			<Button
				icon="sap-icon://edit"
				press="toggleUiModel"
				tooltip="Delete Favorites"
				visible="{ui>/inDisplay}">
			</Button>
		</headerContent>
		<footer>
			<Toolbar
				visible="{ui>/showToolbar}">
				<ToolbarSpacer/>
				<Button
					icon="sap-icon://accept"
					text="done"
					press="toggleUiModel"
					tooltip="Finish Deleting Favorites"
					visible="{ui>/inEdit}">
				</Button>
			</Toolbar>
		</footer>
		<content>
			<List
				id="iconList"
				select="selectIconList"
				delete="deleteIconList"
				noDataText="No favorites yet"
				mode="{ui>/listMode}"
				items="{fav>/icons}">
				<items>
					<StandardListItem
						press="pressIconListItem"
						title="{fav>name}"
						type="{ui>/listItemType}"
						icon="sap-icon://{fav>name}"
						iconInset="true" >
					</StandardListItem>
				</items>
			</List>
		</content>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>

modules.sap/ui/demokit/icex/view/Master.view.xml:
<mvc:View controllerName="sap.ui.demokit.icex.view.Master"
	xmlns="sap.m"
	xmlns:core="sap.ui.core"
	xmlns:mvc="sap.ui.core.mvc"
	xmlns:control="control"
	xmlns:h="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
	<Page
		id="page"
		title="Icon Explorer"
		showFooter="{ui>/showFooter}"
		icon="{img>/icon/ui5}">
		<headerContent>
			<Button
				icon="sap-icon://favorite-list" 
				tooltip="Show Favorites"
				press="toFavorite">
			</Button>
		</headerContent>
		<subHeader>
			<Toolbar>
				<ToolbarSpacer/>
				<SearchField
					id="search"
					placeholder="Search ..."
					liveChange="search"
					tooltip="Search for Icons"
					width="100%">
				</SearchField>
				<ToolbarSpacer/>
			</Toolbar>
		</subHeader>
		<footer>
			<Toolbar>
			</Toolbar>
		</footer>
		<content>
			<!-- This list shows the search results -->
			<List
				id="iconList"
				growing="true"
				select="selectIconList"
				noDataText="No matches for your search"
				mode="{ui>/listMode}"
				growingScrollToLoad="false"
				growingThreshold="{ui>/listPageSize}"
				items="{/groups/0/icons}">  <!-- the first group is assumed to be 'All' -->
				<items>
					<StandardListItem
						title="{name}"
						type="{ui>/listItemType}"
						press="pressIconListItem"
						icon="sap-icon://{name}"
						iconInset="true">
					</StandardListItem>
				</items>
			</List>
			<!-- This list shows the icon groups -->
			<List
				id="groupList"
				headerText="Categories"
				mode="None"
				items="{/groups}">
				<items>
					<StandardListItem
						title="{text}"
						type="Active"
						counter="{count}"
						press="pressGroupListItem"
						iconInset="true">
					</StandardListItem>
				</items>
			</List>
		</content>
	</Page>
</mvc:View>
